# Kuppanna Backend — Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your Uber Direct Sandbox credentials.

## Uber Developer Portal
1. Go to https://developer.uber.com
2. Create an app → enable "Direct" product in Sandbox mode
3. Copy the values below from your app dashboard

```
UBER_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_CLIENT_ID_HERE
UBER_CLIENT_SECRET=YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET_HERE
UBER_CUSTOMER_ID=YOUR_CUSTOMER_ID_HERE
UBER_TOKEN_URL=https://login.uber.com/oauth/v2/token
UBER_API_BASE=https://api.uber.com/v1

PORT=3000
```
